#  History:
#     27-MAR-1991 (HME):
#        Original version.
#     28-MAR-1991 (HME):
#        Help library.
#     11-APR-1991 (HME):
#        Changed some parameter names. Use "Angstrom" instead of "Ang".
#     28-JUN-1991 (HME):
#        Error reporting.
#     28-OCT-1991 (HME):
